    "description": "This first-person horror detective adventure!<br>Go to the abandoned mental hospital and photograph spirits, collect notes, build a chain of events and at the end of the game answer questions related to the events that occurred in this hospital.<br>In this game you have to walk, take pictures, collect notes, it is a horror walking simulator with the ability to take pictures of hidden objects.<br>FEAUTURES:<br>- Retro style graphics with modern post process techniques.<br>- PhotoCamera mode that allows you to see hidden objects inside the game (your photos are saved on your computer).<br>- Interesting plot.<br>- Horror atmosphere with a world that changes around you.<br>- A short experience, like watching a movie.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137910/extras/b3f115547111d85fe555d0880eaeb20e.poster.avif?t=1757651584\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137910/extras/b3f115547111d85fe555d0880eaeb20e.webm?t=1757651584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137910/extras/b3f115547111d85fe555d0880eaeb20e.mp4?t=1757651584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The plot: <br>The year is 1999, you're a Spiritgrapher, a journalist who's dedicated his life to the supernatural. <br>Your camera is able to see beyond the capabilities of the human eye. You can use it to see and photograph ghosts.<br>This time you go to an abandoned hospital rumored to be haunted. <br>Your task is to find out if it is true, to make all the necessary photos, and at the end to put together a story that happened in this hospital.<br><br>Gameplay:<br>Take pictures of the ghosts (the pictures are saved to your computer), collect notes with bits of story.<br>This is a paranormal photojournalist simulator.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137910/extras/ea95881984a692c8424aa855a48e16e0.poster.avif?t=1757651584\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137910/extras/ea95881984a692c8424aa855a48e16e0.webm?t=1757651584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137910/extras/ea95881984a692c8424aa855a48e16e0.mp4?t=1757651584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
